@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Welcome to Ruth Training Company";
}
@section featured {
    <section class="featured">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <hgroup class="title">
                <h1>@ViewBag.Title.</h1>
                <h2>@ViewBag.Message</h2>
            </hgroup>
            <p>

                At Ruth Training Company, we are passionate about empowering professionals through top-notch seminars and training courses. Our diverse range of courses is designed to cater to various industries and skill levels, ensuring that every participant leaves with valuable knowledge and practical skills.

                Each course is thoughtfully crafted and delivered by our experienced staff members at convenient locations, from our internal seminar room S10 to the elegant Hilton Hotel Suite 100. We understand the value of flexible learning, which is why our courses accommodate both individual delegates and groups from companies.

                Our fee structure is tailored to provide excellent value, with discounts for multiple attendees from the same organization. For example, while the first delegate is charged $1000, the second can attend for just $750. This makes it easier for companies to invest in the professional growth of their teams.

                When you register for a course, whether as an individual or through your company, our dedicated team ensures a smooth registration process. We also take care of invoicing, making it easy for you or your company to manage payments.

                Explore our course offerings today and take the next step in your professional journey with Ruth Training Company. Let's grow together!
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
}

